OL,7,FLeanne Lucas, a yoga instructor whose
OL,8,FTaylor Swift-themed dance class was
OL,9,Ftargeted last July, has launched a new
OL,10,Fcampaign called Let's Be Blunt that
OL,11,Fshe hopes will save lives.
OL,13,FThe Southport attacker was armed with
OL,14,Fa kitchen knife he'd bought online.
OL,16,FThe attack claimed the lives of three
OL,17,Fgirls, while Leanne, local businessman
OL,18,FJohn Hayes, and eight children were
OL,19,Ftreated in hospital for serious
OL,20,Finjuries.
