OL,7,FHe was later jailed for a minimum of
OL,8,F52 years for the three murders, as
OL,9,Fwell as the attempted murders of
OL,10,FLeanne Lucas, businessman John Hayes,
OL,11,Fand eight other children who survived
OL,12,Ftheir injuries.
OL,14,FToday, the 36-year-old's new
OL,15,Finitiative is calling for the
OL,16,Fwidespread adoption of rounded-tip
OL,17,Fkitchen knives to reduce knife-related
OL,18,Fviolence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
