OL,4,C'blunt' knives to prevent more
OL,5,Ctragedies
OL,7,FShe told ITV News that we need to
OL,8,F"change the perception" of knives
OL,9,Fafter she was critically injured
OL,10,Fherself.
OL,12,F"In my eyes I don't see change
OL,13,Fhappening fast enough," she said. "Are
OL,14,Fwe waiting for the next incident to
OL,15,Fappear on the TV? I'm not prepared to
OL,16,Fdo that."
