OL,7,FLet's Be Blunt campaign calls on
OL,8,Fhouseholds, retailers, manufacturers,
OL,9,Fand policymakers to switch from
OL,10,Fpointed kitchen knives to safer,
OL,11,Frounded-tip alternatives.
OL,13,FLeanne said: "The kitchen utensil has
OL,14,Fthe potential to become a weapon - I'm
OL,15,Fasking people to take an inventory of
OL,16,Ftheir kitchen... so that your kitchen
OL,17,Fbecomes a safer place. It reduces the
OL,18,Frisk, reduces the impulsivity, and
OL,19,Fhopefully goes towards preventing
OL,20,Fknife crime in the future occurring."
