OL,7,FSix-year-old Bebe King, seven-year-old
OL,8,FElsie Dot Stancombe, and nine-year-old
OL,9,FAlice da Silva Aguiar were killed
OL,10,Fduring the stabbing.
OL,12,FLeanne told ITV News that she has
OL,13,Flaunched her campaign not only for the
OL,14,Fthree girls, but "for everyone"
OL,15,Ftelling us "it's for them, the
OL,16,Finjured, and their families supporting
OL,17,Fthem".
