OL,5,Ctragedies
OL,7,FShe added: "Every day the girls are in
OL,8,Fmy thoughts, if we can do something to
OL,9,Fhelp this not happen to other
OL,10,Fchildren, that's what we're going to
OL,11,Fdo."
OL,13,FHer life has changed since the
OL,14,Fincident, telling ITV News that she
OL,15,F"had no purpose" and "didn't know what
OL,16,Fto do" but has now found a passion to
OL,17,Fgive her and other people hope.
