OL,7,FThe latest ONS homicide statistics
OL,8,Fshowed there were 262 murders
OL,9,Finvolving a knife or sharp instrument
OL,10,Fin England and Wales in the year to
OL,11,FMarch 2024, with 17 of the victims
OL,12,Fbeing children under the age of 16.
OL,14,FKitchen knives were used in 44% of
OL,15,Fthose incidents.
