OL,7,FTaking her campaign to parliament,
OL,8,FLeanne will give a speech at a special
OL,9,Freception in the presence of Home
OL,10,FSecretary Yvette Cooper.
OL,12,FThe event is part of Knife Crime
OL,13,FAwareness Week and has been organised
OL,14,Fby the Ben Kinsella Trust, a charity
OL,15,Fset up in memory of 16-year-old Ben
OL,16,FKinsella, who was stabbed to death in
OL,17,FLondon in 2008.
