OL,7,FCrime and Policing Minister, Dame
OL,8,FDiana Johnson, has said that "nothing
OL,9,Fis off the table when it comes to
OL,10,Fgetting lethal blades off our streets
OL,11,Fand keeping people safe" and that the
OL,12,Fgovernment is exploring options to
OL,13,Fmake changes by meeting with retailers
OL,14,Fand manufacturers.
OL,16,FFor more information on the Let's Be
OL,17,FBlunt campaign visit
OL,18,Fwww.letsbeblunt.co.uk.
